------------------

Input data: 234 taxa with 5 partitions and 2475 total sites (0.675473% missing data)

  ID	Type	Seq	Site	Unique	Infor	Invar	Const	Name
   1	DNA	234	407	186	75	291	291	sia
   2	DNA	234	517	198	98	395	395	bdnf
   3	DNA	234	555	252	122	362	362	nxc
   4	DNA	233	510	364	315	172	172	cyb
   5	DNA	227	486	393	340	112	112	nd4

Column meanings:
  Unique: Number of unique site patterns
  Infor:  Number of parsimony-informative sites
  Invar:  Number of invariant sites
  Const:  Number of constant sites (can be subset of invariant sites)

